<h2 class="bold font-l">Asterix: Mansions of the Gods</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
This CGI-animated movie of Asterix begins with a minimalist 2D title sequence. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnimatedCreditsOpening" class='trope-example-link'>Animated Credits Opening</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="1uccrc" data-video-descrip="Asterix and Obelix don't give the Roman soldiers a chance to get at least get one victory in battle." data-video-title="Asterix: Mansions of the Gods" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/1uccrc_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1uccrc.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/CurbStompBattle" data-video-tropename="Curb-Stomp Battle" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/TheMansionsOfTheGods" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/1uccrc.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Asterix: Mansio...</span></p>
</a>
